name: Contractor wise CL Costing Report
query:
SELECT 
`tabContract Labour Costing`.`contractor` AS "Contractor::250", 
sum(`tabContract Labour Costing`.`total_working_hours`) AS `Total Working Hours:Float:150`, 
sum(`tabContract Labour Costing`.`actual_working_hours`) AS `Actual Working Hours:Float:150`, 
ROUND(sum(`tabContract Labour Costing`.`earned_ctc`)) AS `Earned CTC:Currency:100`, 
ROUND(sum(`tabContract Labour Costing`.`ot_hours`)) AS `OT Hours:Float:100`, 
ROUND(sum(`tabContract Labour Costing`.`ot_earnings`)) AS `OT Earnings:Currency:100`,
ROUND(sum(`tabContract Labour Costing`.`total`)) AS `TOTAL:Currency:100`
FROM `tabContract Labour Costing`
GROUP BY 
`tabContract Labour Costing`.`contractor`;
